#### 2.6.2 RELEASE ###########################################################

2007-07-05 Jens Langner <Jens.Langner@light-speed.de>

  * CECATDirectory.cpp: fixed matrixParamsValid() macro which made incorrect
    assumptions about the minimum/maximum allowed numbers for frame/plane/gate
    bed and data number specifiers. This could have ended up in not being 
    able to write/read all minimum/maximum allowed frames, for example.

