    (returned scan start time instead of dosestart time)

2007-06-26 Jens Langner <Jens.Langner@light-speed.de>

  * examples/ecatcmp: added calculation of min/max count statistic

2007-06-05 Hagen Moelle <draggore@gmx.de>

  * ecatutil: sets filter values in subheader of smoother processed image file
    when called with -b

