#### 2.2.6 RELEASE ###########################################################

2006-06-07 Jens Langner <Jens.Langner@light-speed.de>

	* src/helpers/MedIOUnits: removed all tr() uses and also the formerly
		necessary QObject derivation. This should make the helps classes
		much more simple and intuitive.
	* src/helpers/MedIOUnits.cpp: enhanced and fixed the setUnitFromString()
		functions to use else branches for a faster identification routine.
	* src/helpers/MedIOUnits.h: removed all inline functions and
		put the functions into a new MedIOUnits.cpp source file so
		that in future no recompilation is required in case a minor
		bug is fixed.
  * examples/ecat/ecatutil: added a new example tool 'ecatutil'
		which allows to strip a specific matrix from an ECAT file,
		but also allows to add a new, empty matrix to a file. It should
		illustrate how to use CECATDirectory/CECATDirectoryItem
		directly.
	* src/ecat/CECATDirectoryItem.h: moved the matrixID macros out
		of the private header area so that application can directly use
		those macros.

